    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >美乐谜音（MeloMisterio）是一款以克服障碍、抵达终点为目标的平台游戏，但它最大的特色是：你的动作声音会变成旋律，而你可以用这些旋律来操控机关。<br>这将带来一种全新的音乐体验——只要玩动作游戏，就能同时演奏音乐。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >声音化为旋律的爽快操作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你演奏的旋律来操控机关</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的音乐互动与演出效果，进一步加深音乐体验</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >声音化为旋律的爽快操作</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在美乐谜音中，跳跃、冲刺等所有动作都对应两种按键。<br>其中一个会沿着音阶播放比上一段旋律高一级的音，另一个则会播放低一级的音。<br>通过组合操作，音符会在上下移动中形成旋律。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这种系统让每一次输入都充满爽快感，带来如同即兴演奏般的游玩体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/d2880e1ca9dfc2f1bcfb3e16a96e7da8.poster.avif?t=1771166162\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/d2880e1ca9dfc2f1bcfb3e16a96e7da8.webm?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/d2880e1ca9dfc2f1bcfb3e16a96e7da8.mp4?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用你演奏的旋律来操控机关</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升高或降低旋律，并不只是为了发出声音。<br>在某些关卡中，你需要通过改变旋律来操控机关——例如让栅栏和升降台上下或左右移动，或让它们旋转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >演奏旋律，打开通往终点的道路吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/ea40a71d1262c75c22e27023acca848c.poster.avif?t=1771166162\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/ea40a71d1262c75c22e27023acca848c.webm?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/ea40a71d1262c75c22e27023acca848c.mp4?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/70b8377299a0d2959aae26b536b2a189.poster.avif?t=1771166162\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/70b8377299a0d2959aae26b536b2a189.webm?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/70b8377299a0d2959aae26b536b2a189.mp4?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/715014167a8ea03f157668140049279d.poster.avif?t=1771166162\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/715014167a8ea03f157668140049279d.webm?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/715014167a8ea03f157668140049279d.mp4?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的音乐互动与演出效果，进一步加深音乐体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了旋律操控机关之外，游戏中还有许多音乐相关的互动与演出效果，例如会跟随节奏移动的墙壁，或是拾取后会演奏对旋律的音符等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感受音乐、享受旅程，并抵达终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/56d279cf6125e059b1b04b26a63fc91f.poster.avif?t=1771166162\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/56d279cf6125e059b1b04b26a63fc91f.webm?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/56d279cf6125e059b1b04b26a63fc91f.mp4?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/5d1ed7a5fa8e28511bf085578c6491d6.poster.avif?t=1771166162\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/5d1ed7a5fa8e28511bf085578c6491d6.webm?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3099880/extras/5d1ed7a5fa8e28511bf085578c6491d6.mp4?t=1771166162\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
